{"tid":1731554,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屌佢老母班狗話要六四重演","createTime":"2019-11-17T17:58:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T05:53:10.000Z","uid":200113,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9d97eb9387bfa045cfafa37a2ed4a4c778b173b2","tid":1731554,"uid":200113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T17:58:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">國際文宣</span></span><br />\n<br />\n【防暴警口出狂言 聲稱要重演六四屠城】<br />\n<br />\n警方昨晚(17日)於大埔與市民發生口角期間，有防暴警察一度指要「去Poly劏曱甴」，甚至妄言要令「六四重演」，其言論頓時引起現場人士起哄。<br />\n<br />\n影片來源：中大校園電台<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/219478461572330/posts/1231683680351798?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F219478461572330%2Fposts%2F1231683680351798%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=RPOps9CZsjru%2Bb3lYBIKGoLj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=d8bdfd70\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/219478461572330/posts/1231683680351798?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">屌你啦死黑警 係唔係要殺撚哂全香港先安落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要間接幫中共承認六四係有大屠殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你話班毅進狗係咪真係賤過狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"2a197348cf4bb51423e2cc80bc06918c267d3b5c","tid":1731554,"uid":200113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T18:06:35.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"ed84d0ebf8befbb54d7b16070fc068db8f1b9b2b","tid":1731554,"uid":200113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T